# Optional. If unset, the app calls same-origin /api (see frontend/vercel.json and
# public/_redirects) so the browser never cross-origin calls Render — most reliable.
#
# Set only if you deploy the SPA somewhere without rewrites (e.g. raw GitHub Pages)
# or you want to talk to the API directly:
#   https://your-service.onrender.com     (we auto-append /api)
#   https://your-service.onrender.com/api (explicit)
#
# HTTPS page + http:// API is upgraded to https:// where possible (mixed content).
#
# Vite inlines VITE_* at build time — change env then rebuild.

# VITE_API_URL=https://eventify-6gzq.onrender.com/api

# Emergency override (no rebuild): in index.html add before src/main.jsx:
# <script>window.__EVENTIFY_API_URL__="https://your-api.com/api"</script>
